{
  "page": "Anniversary Tourney",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Anniversary Tourney</b> was a great <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_272_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">272&#160;AC</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anniversary_Tourney&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, hosted the tourney to celebrate the tenth year of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>'s reign. During its proceedings the king drunkenly insulted Tywin's wife, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Joanna_Lannister\" title=\"Joanna Lannister\">Joanna Lannister</a>, by asking if her breasts had been ruined by breastfeeding her children, <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a>. Aerys refused to allow Tywin to resign as Hand the following day.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>It was oft believed that the lavish prizes offered in the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Harrenhal\" title=\"Tourney at Harrenhal\">tourney at Harrenhal</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281&#160;AC</a> was an attempt by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walter_Whent\" title=\"Walter Whent\">Walter Whent</a> to outdo Tywin's tourney in 272.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_fall_of_the_dragons:_the_year_of_the_false_spring.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_fall_of_the_dragons:_the_year_of_the_false_spring.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anniversary_Tourney&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">A Forum of Ice and Fire: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/topic/119534-twoiaf-spoilers-inconsistency-or-intentional/page-17#entry6428144\">TWOIAF Spoilers Inconsistency or Intentional?</a>, November 7, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings: Aerys II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_fall_of_the_dragons:_the_year_of_the_false_spring.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_fall_of_the_dragons:_the_year_of_the_false_spring.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Fall of the Dragons: The Year of the False Spring.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403103704\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.035 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.115 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 207/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8663/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1028/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 446/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1792/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.020/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   67.838      1 -total\n 79.85%   54.167      2 Template:Date\n 14.77%   10.022      2 Template:Ref\n  9.97%    6.763      2 Template:Ref/core\n  4.55%    3.085      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19815-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403103703 and revision id 332917\n -->\n",
